title: Californication Season 2 Complete
description:
Complete Season 2 of Californication

Californication is a Showtime TV series production created by Tom Kapinos, starring David Duchovny as Hank Moody: a troubled novelist whose move to California and his writer's block complicate the relationships with his ex-girlfriend Karen (Natascha McElhone) and daughter Becca (Madeleine Martin).


Episodes:

1) Slip of the Tongue
2) The Great Ashby
3) No Way To Treat A Lady
4) The Raw & the Cooked
5) Vaginatown
6) Coke Dick & First Kick
7) In a Lonely Place
8) Going Down and Out in Beverly Hills
9) La Ronde
10) In Utero
11) Blues From Laurel Canyon
12) La Petite Mort
